works.description: Founded by David Nelken in 1897, the modern heritage brand Globe-Trotter has always stunned the world with its true craftsmanship and quality luggage. The house has catered to leisure and business travelers for a long time with the finest in luggage. On the other hand, New York tobacconist Nat Sherman, which started in 1930, has earned a name in the worldwide tobacco industry for its quality cigars and cigarettes. To celebrate the decades of success achieved by Nat Sherman, Globe-Trotter has designed an exclusive humidor.
